name: Crocs Kids-boy Electro Green Sandals
description:
Originally designed for boaters and fishermen to have a firm foot even on slippery surfaces, crocs has gone a long way in creating footwear for those who demand complete comfort. Replete with several benefits such as the shoe moulding to your feet using your body heat, it's a hot favourite for little feet.

The speciality of these shoes are that they need to Fit loosely around the feet, such that neither the sides of the shoe nor the toe unit come in contact with the feet. Instead, there should be a quarter to half inch gap between the foot and the wall of the shoe, and you should be able to comfortably fit a finger between the heel and back strap.

Upper
EVA upper with textured inside for lightweight feel, comfort and durability
EVA material that moulds to the foot shape offering ample ergonomic comfort
Perforations on the forefoot for ventilation, to drain away water and to add jibbitz – decorations for your crocs
Back strap to support the ankle and hold the foot in place
Upper moulded to midsole for comfort and protection of feet from abrasion
Broad EVA lining along the midsole for enhanced durability
Brand button on upper for style

Midsole
EVA footbed with horizontal and foot shaped lines for ergonomic comfort and acupressure
Crocs branding on the back heel
Fungus, bacteria and odour resistant for a healthy wear even in wet conditions
Mild heel cup on the footbed to support the heel

Outsole
Slip resistant outsole with multi-directional textured grooves in the forefoot and backfoot

Shoe care
Rub surface with clean, damp cloth to remove dust

The nike Lunarfly+ 2 running shoe has a more robust heel counter than its predecessor for an improved fit around the heel. Inside the breathable mesh upper is an innersleeve, or bootie, that wraps around the foot for a snug, breathable feel and easy on and off. Soft meets springy - the Lunarlon cushioning system is made up of a soft yet resilient foam core encased within a supportive foam carrier for a unique, lightweight blend of ultra-plush cushioning, springy response and support. The midsole of this running shoe features Dynamic Support, which adapts to your stride throughout each run to provide just the right amount of support. Best for underpronated to mildly overpronated gait types.

Midsole
Lunarlon cushioning for soft yet responsive shock absorption – 30% lighter than the traditional Phylon

Outsole
Outsole flex grooves for enhanced flexibility and a smooth, efficient stride
A mix of rubbers in a Waffle pattern on the outsole for durability and traction
